<li>I cleaned and uploaded data from the <a href="https://urbaninstitute.github.io/nccs/datasets/bmf/">Business Master File (BMF)</a>, including only data with an A25 (Arts Education) NTEE (National Taxonomy of Exempt Entities) code.</li>
